Your grain was delivered there.

40:30.162 --> 40:33.797
Compliments of
catherine de medici.

40:33.799 --> 40:35.999
Hmm.

40:37.535 --> 40:39.669
I hear the townspeople
are toasting your name--

40:39.671 --> 40:41.504
Their savior.

40:41.506 --> 40:46.109
But they're not the first
to benefit from your generosity.

40:46.111 --> 40:48.578
A church rebuilt,
a new well dug.

40:48.580 --> 40:52.515
And each town more grateful
to you than the last.

40:52.517 --> 40:53.783
I do what I have to do.

40:53.785 --> 40:55.018
For the people.

40:55.020 --> 40:56.519
You do it for yourself.

40:56.521 --> 40:58.688
To ensure that you're loved,
protected,

40:58.690 --> 41:00.924
By at least some
within the realm.

41:00.926 --> 41:03.660
For when francis and mary
produce an heir,

41:03.662 --> 41:05.528
And all your other children
move to the back of the line,

41:05.530 --> 41:07.630
And you with them.

41:07.632 --> 41:10.600
I don't see that happening
any time soon.

41:10.602 --> 41:12.602
Because mary hasn't fallen
pregnant yet?

41:14.205 --> 41:16.005
It can happen
in the blink of an eye.

